          <p>I just wanted to thank you for this opportunity, for seeing something in my previous work or myself that warranted you giving me the chance to undertake this test. It’s been a fun challenge and I’m truly appreciative of the opportunity. Your work is an inspiration and your website is truly awesome, it’s so impressive and to potentially have the chance to work with is exciting and truly would be an honour.</p>
          <p>Please feel free to check out my <a href="https://www.michaeljcaunce.com/" target="__blank">website</a> and if you need anything, let me know.</p>
